metadata.description: "A Somewhat Strange Story" Participates in a unique quest through different levels of reality. The Earth Down and the Earth Up, the opposites levels of reality, and the mysterious Time Fluid. Are you confused? We are too. Purchase our unique Skull Guy NFT, and redeem a copy of the first release of the comic book "A Somewhat Strange Story". Follow the adventures of SG and his funny dog.
